3. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper may involve computer vision techniques for object recognition and tracking during the manipulation process. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper may involve machine learning techniques for learning grasp configurations and object manipulation strategies. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper may involve control theory and system design for the dual-arm manipulation system.
